---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Mod Commissions — Wenji Makes" description="Custom Stardew Valley mod development by Wenji.">
  <article class="content-page">
    <h1>Mod Commissions</h1>
    <p>Have a gameplay idea but don’t code, or simply don’t have time to build it? I take custom mod commissions.</p>

    <h2>What I can make</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>New gameplay mechanics, survival modes, systems, and automation</li>
      <li>Maps, NPCs, story events, and progression</li>
      <li>Custom tools, weapons, and interactive items</li>
      <li>Extensions or ports of existing mods, when technically feasible</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Tell me what you want to make — concrete examples help</li>
      <li>I review feasibility and propose scope, price, and timeline</li>
      <li>Once we agree, I start development</li>
      <li>You receive the finished mod with basic usage instructions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Supported games</h2>
    <p>I currently focus on <strong>Stardew Valley</strong> using SMAPI and Content Patcher. Ideas for other games are welcome for discussion.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:32px;padding:24px;background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center;">
      <p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text);">Have an idea? Tell me about it.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:16px;">Include the game version, what the mod should do, references, budget range, and preferred timeline.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="mailto:wenjistudios@gmail.com?subject=Mod%20commission%20inquiry" class="btn btn-primary">Email Wenji</a>
        <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/users/179201778" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline">Message on Nexus Mods</a>
        <a href="https://ko-fi.com/wenjimods" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="kofi-btn">Ko-fi</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
